on to serve. Finally, numerical evidence on the benefits of\nAC OPF modeling intertemporal transformer life degradation suggests that it may\nbe worth considering the introduction of intra-day markets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2019 16:37:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-05"}
