m. When including only the PMT time resolution, but no further\nelectronics simulation and waveform reconstruction, the exposure loss is only\n1%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2019 10:02:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
