ed. Stronger\ndrivers lead to higher vales of the line width estimated energy fluxes.\nFinally, estimations of the energy fluxes by spectroscopic data are affected by\nthe LOS angle, favoring combined analysis of imaging and spectroscopic data for\nsingle oscillating loops.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2019 12:50:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-06"}
